title: NASA Selects Shawn Quinn to Lead Exploration Ground Systems Program
summary: NASA has selected Shawn Quinn as manager of the Exploration Ground Systems program based at the agency’s Kennedy Space Center in Florida, effective Sunday, Jan. 15.

title: SpaceX edges closer to first Starship orbital launch attempt
